### 2. No Helmet (Missing Security Headers)

The app sets **no HTTP security headers**. This leaves it vulnerable to clickjacking, MIME-sniffing, XSS (if HTML is ever served), and other browser-side attacks.

**Risk:** OWASP A05:2021 — Security Misconfiguration

**Recommendation:**

